Usage: check_ufc [-help] <fn> [-report_file <string>] [-report_unplaced_block] [ -selected_rules <string>] [ -include_all_rules ]

-help                        # Prints out the command usage
<fn>                         # Specify filename (string, required)
-include_all_rules           # Specify whether tool report all rules' summary
                             # of violations. (bool, optional)
-report_file <string>        # Specify file name which tool will puts the
                             # summary of violations. (string, optional)
-report_unplaced_block       # Enable tool to show the number of unplaced
                             # macros in summary (bool, optional)
-selected_rules <string>     # selected rules only (string, optional)